{"4265410": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "純真少女的魔界冒險", "steam_appid": 4265410, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a1477a08cc6458975b33e65de0cf3b0c.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某個遙遠的世界，出現了一名強大的「魔人」，將世界的一個部分連同城鎮、居民、還有所有一切都吞噬進了名為「魔空」的魔法空間裡。為了取回他們的世界，無數的勇者成為了魔人狩獵者前往魔空討伐魔人，然而卻沒有一個人平安回來…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到一位預言家預言：世界終將出現一位少女，她會成為最強的魔人狩獵者打倒魔人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而這位被稱為「預言之子」的少女，在眾人的期待下成長成了勇敢的戰士，如今已經踏上討伐魔人的征途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在另一個遙遠的小鎮裡，一位與預言沒有任何關聯，單純就是憧憬著成為帥氣魔人狩獵者的少女「愛莉」，抱著天真爛漫的幻想，也開始了她的冒險。首先她要做的，就是友善的強迫徵用貓人族貓娘的家當作基地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而她，就是這個故事的主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/efaa746b12bf33e32aeafc6e7fde3bb2.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/976328f6089c74330d07ab4fc8ddf925.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D動作冒險遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愛莉(玩家)將前往一個又一個不一樣的魔空副本探索與戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎副本關卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有8個主線關卡，以及5個支線挑戰關卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個關卡又分為不同的探索區域，以及Boss戰區域，合計多達35個地圖供玩家探索與戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b91d1d8a7aeeba4ea377afcf076c35b3.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b91d1d8a7aeeba4ea377afcf076c35b3.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b91d1d8a7aeeba4ea377afcf076c35b3.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎敵人種類</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有一般怪物、陷阱、Boss怪總計32種怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分怪物擁有拘束色色技能，如果在戰鬥中不小心被抓住的話…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/94ed1af3797bcfd44e4ae1e1fbb9d7c8.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/94ed1af3797bcfd44e4ae1e1fbb9d7c8.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/94ed1af3797bcfd44e4ae1e1fbb9d7c8.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎大量的色色內容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了戰鬥中的拘束色色3D動畫之外。還有多達37張的戰敗CG劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >對象以異種怪物與陷阱為主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含拘束、觸手、捕食、丸吞、榨乳、吸收、苗床、狀態變化、催情等等的情境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/6899cd1dc223bacea189131761d6830d.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/6899cd1dc223bacea189131761d6830d.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/6899cd1dc223bacea189131761d6830d.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎劍×槍 多元豐富的戰鬥體驗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基本的戰鬥就包括了近距離的劍技與遠距離的槍砲兩大系統。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能依照地形與怪物種類隨時自由切換。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a8c97fb509ba0b58f75d77185e6ec93e.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a8c97fb509ba0b58f75d77185e6ec93e.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a8c97fb509ba0b58f75d77185e6ec93e.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著角色逐漸成長，並攻略更多副本，除了能夠使用關卡中獲得的寶石來強化角色能力之外，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以學習更多新的劍技，以及獲得各式各樣的槍枝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥過程中透過滑鼠左右鍵短按、長按，與方向鍵的組合，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就能夠使出不同的強力招式，與切換擁有的槍枝種類。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/57bb8fdcb46dd21e6c18d944168f2822.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=626 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/57bb8fdcb46dd21e6c18d944168f2822.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/57bb8fdcb46dd21e6c18d944168f2822.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，在地圖探索的過程，也能獲得砲彈、砲台、治療空間等等有趣的特殊道具，能夠在戰鬥中起到意想不到的輔助功效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎換裝系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在副本探索的過程中可以拾獲各種不同的裝備。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含武器、皮膚、上半身、下半身、手部、腿部、背部、內褲等等不同部位的服裝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/078b746f5051db05637e7f03bde5d69a.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/078b746f5051db05637e7f03bde5d69a.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/078b746f5051db05637e7f03bde5d69a.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配上3D空間中能夠自由變換視角的機能，讓探索與戰鬥過程隨時可以賞心悅目一番。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/2fb755a272af89b5c5afdafa8aa5d1cb.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/2fb755a272af89b5c5afdafa8aa5d1cb.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/2fb755a272af89b5c5afdafa8aa5d1cb.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/358970ba58734d26aa759dd4d43efb40.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/67dd6102af0674e56f591ab8b9db5cfb.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/f4bf2bbdb96324417720f3159e203d1b.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/437cc5b803793b90d07b00492778c807.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/fa25b65243a32a8a9afc8ddbb2207663.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b90f019ea1294ad03b10805c877bc42a.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >副本地圖有多層結構與許多隱藏道路及可蒐集的物品，如果善用地形也能更安全有效率地擊敗敵人，探索與戰鬥過程有趣不枯燥。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富的HCG，共有37張HCG，還有差分、額外CG與立繪。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能夠自由調整四種難易度，也擁有作弊模式可以快速通關。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不需要真的戰敗也能夠在回想房間解鎖戰敗CG。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遠距離槍彈攻擊能搭配自動瞄準功能，不擅長射擊遊戲也能快速上手。</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a1477a08cc6458975b33e65de0cf3b0c.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某個遙遠的世界，出現了一名強大的「魔人」，將世界的一個部分連同城鎮、居民、還有所有一切都吞噬進了名為「魔空」的魔法空間裡。為了取回他們的世界，無數的勇者成為了魔人狩獵者前往魔空討伐魔人，然而卻沒有一個人平安回來…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到一位預言家預言：世界終將出現一位少女，她會成為最強的魔人狩獵者打倒魔人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而這位被稱為「預言之子」的少女，在眾人的期待下成長成了勇敢的戰士，如今已經踏上討伐魔人的征途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在另一個遙遠的小鎮裡，一位與預言沒有任何關聯，單純就是憧憬著成為帥氣魔人狩獵者的少女「愛莉」，抱著天真爛漫的幻想，也開始了她的冒險。首先她要做的，就是友善的強迫徵用貓人族貓娘的家當作基地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而她，就是這個故事的主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/efaa746b12bf33e32aeafc6e7fde3bb2.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/976328f6089c74330d07ab4fc8ddf925.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D動作冒險遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愛莉(玩家)將前往一個又一個不一樣的魔空副本探索與戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎副本關卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有8個主線關卡，以及5個支線挑戰關卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個關卡又分為不同的探索區域，以及Boss戰區域，合計多達35個地圖供玩家探索與戰鬥。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b91d1d8a7aeeba4ea377afcf076c35b3.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b91d1d8a7aeeba4ea377afcf076c35b3.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b91d1d8a7aeeba4ea377afcf076c35b3.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎敵人種類</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有一般怪物、陷阱、Boss怪總計32種怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分怪物擁有拘束色色技能，如果在戰鬥中不小心被抓住的話…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/94ed1af3797bcfd44e4ae1e1fbb9d7c8.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/94ed1af3797bcfd44e4ae1e1fbb9d7c8.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/94ed1af3797bcfd44e4ae1e1fbb9d7c8.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎大量的色色內容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了戰鬥中的拘束色色3D動畫之外。還有多達37張的戰敗CG劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >對象以異種怪物與陷阱為主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含拘束、觸手、捕食、丸吞、榨乳、吸收、苗床、狀態變化、催情等等的情境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/6899cd1dc223bacea189131761d6830d.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/6899cd1dc223bacea189131761d6830d.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/6899cd1dc223bacea189131761d6830d.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎劍×槍 多元豐富的戰鬥體驗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基本的戰鬥就包括了近距離的劍技與遠距離的槍砲兩大系統。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能依照地形與怪物種類隨時自由切換。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a8c97fb509ba0b58f75d77185e6ec93e.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a8c97fb509ba0b58f75d77185e6ec93e.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/a8c97fb509ba0b58f75d77185e6ec93e.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著角色逐漸成長，並攻略更多副本，除了能夠使用關卡中獲得的寶石來強化角色能力之外，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以學習更多新的劍技，以及獲得各式各樣的槍枝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在戰鬥過程中透過滑鼠左右鍵短按、長按，與方向鍵的組合，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就能夠使出不同的強力招式，與切換擁有的槍枝種類。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/57bb8fdcb46dd21e6c18d944168f2822.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=626 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/57bb8fdcb46dd21e6c18d944168f2822.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/57bb8fdcb46dd21e6c18d944168f2822.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，在地圖探索的過程，也能獲得砲彈、砲台、治療空間等等有趣的特殊道具，能夠在戰鬥中起到意想不到的輔助功效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◎換裝系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在副本探索的過程中可以拾獲各種不同的裝備。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含武器、皮膚、上半身、下半身、手部、腿部、背部、內褲等等不同部位的服裝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/078b746f5051db05637e7f03bde5d69a.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/078b746f5051db05637e7f03bde5d69a.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/078b746f5051db05637e7f03bde5d69a.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配上3D空間中能夠自由變換視角的機能，讓探索與戰鬥過程隨時可以賞心悅目一番。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/2fb755a272af89b5c5afdafa8aa5d1cb.poster.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/2fb755a272af89b5c5afdafa8aa5d1cb.webm?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/2fb755a272af89b5c5afdafa8aa5d1cb.mp4?t=1776754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/358970ba58734d26aa759dd4d43efb40.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/67dd6102af0674e56f591ab8b9db5cfb.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/f4bf2bbdb96324417720f3159e203d1b.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/437cc5b803793b90d07b00492778c807.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/fa25b65243a32a8a9afc8ddbb2207663.avif?t=1776754319\" width=1560 height=1170 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/extras/b90f019ea1294ad03b10805c877bc42a.avif?t=1776754319\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >副本地圖有多層結構與許多隱藏道路及可蒐集的物品，如果善用地形也能更安全有效率地擊敗敵人，探索與戰鬥過程有趣不枯燥。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豐富的HCG，共有37張HCG，還有差分、額外CG與立繪。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能夠自由調整四種難易度，也擁有作弊模式可以快速通關。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不需要真的戰敗也能夠在回想房間解鎖戰敗CG。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遠距離槍彈攻擊能搭配自動瞄準功能，不擅長射擊遊戲也能快速上手。</p></li></ul>", "short_description": "3D動作冒險遊戲。愛莉(玩家)將前往一個又一個不一樣的關卡副本探索與戰鬥。 擁有劍×槍兩種戰鬥模式與技能組合，豐富多樣的地圖關卡設計，以及32種異種怪物與色色陷阱。", "supported_languages": "日文<strong>*</strong>, 英文, 韓文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/e4b111b4787e51496a6bcc40257055a177bb5506/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776754319", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/605b5a4b2f25ca147b67a6b5e46ae82dca0ccd17/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776754319", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4265410/605b5a4b2f25ca147b67a6b5e46ae82dca0ccd17/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776754319", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 3 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64bit OS<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Core i5<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GTX 650 Ti<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 3 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "All characters are above 18.", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 3 季"}}}}